    {
      "text": "Super Star Force: Jikūreki no Himitsu (スーパースターフォース 時空暦の秘密; lit. \"Secrets of the Space-Time Calendar\") is a vertically-scrolling shoot 'em up adventure video game developed and published by Tecmo on November 11, 1986 for the Family Computer only in Japan.\nThe game was featured in episode 111 (14th Season) of GameCenter CX.\nWhile this video game was originally assigned by Hudson Soft to be the publisher, Tecmo (then known as Tehkan) decided to both develop and publish the game as they were the official copyright owners.",
